PM pms5003 i2c driver
=====================

Authors
--------

RIOT-OS implementation for Plantower PMS 5003 series I2C dust sensors.
The I2C bus is probed for the sensor. The reading is synchronous running
in a separate thread. THe implementation has been tested against the
PMS 5003i (I2C)


